20220817 eRVin version updated to latest downloadfrom the above link

image-backup.bak is the original version with MNTPATH="/tmp/img-backup-mnt/"

image-backup is a version modified with MNTPATH="/media/pi/ervinos/img-backup-mnt/"

This was done to prevent the error "Unable to unmount image ROOT partition" when
trying to umount /tmp/img-backup-mnt/

See the image-backup file comments for details.
